ps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Cumulative_average">cumulative mo=
ving average</a>.
</p><p>The period selected (<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-elemen=
t-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=
